<bibRefCitation author="Andersen" box="[769,957,1585,1610]" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" refString="Andersen, N. M. (1995) Infraorder Gerromorpha Popov, 1971 - semiaquatic bugs, pp. 17 - 114. In: Aukema, B. &amp; Rieger, C. (Eds.), Catalogue of the Heteroptera of the Palaearctic Region. Vol. 1. Enicocephalomorpha, Dipsocoromorpha, Nepomorpha, Gerromorpha and Leptopodomorpha. The Netherlands Entomological Society, Amsterdam, xxvi + 222 pp." type="book chapter" year="1995">
